snippet.textDisplay:
To,
The people who have nothing good to do other than saying that these two artists copied each other.


Okay now, Billie and Melanie, both are incredible, amazingly talented people, They have their own different style.
If this is about the title, There are freaking several songs that have the same title. even if its the song, I mean listen to the lyrics and the music, they are totally different.
If this is about the style, just so you know, they are from different times and I think no one copied anyone here. I have a feeling after this becomes a huge fight they both are gonna be like " oh I knew you existed honestly such a huge coincidence that our fans would think stuff like that"
I would also like to say, If you are gonna argue about this, then argue with facts*, and actual *knowledge about both of the artist. Dont go saying 'yes she copied' and 'no she didnt'.
(in some cases) Don't come here for attention, just cause everyone is saying doesnt mean you have to as well.
Now, If you have any objections relating this. Please, humor me. I would love to listen to you blabber


From,
A fellow CryLash
